title: 310. Andy & DJ CTI: Biden Threatens Oil Companies, Squid Game Reality Show & Democrat Predicts Civil War
itunes:title: 310. Andy & DJ CTI: Biden Threatens Oil Companies, Squid Game Reality Show & Democrat Predicts Civil War
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss President Biden sending a letter to oil companies threatening to use emergency powers if they don't increase production, Netflix teasing a 'Squid Game' reality competition show with $4.56 million in prize money, and a New York Democrat predicting a civil war if Republicans take power in the November mid-terms.
